result.adr_address: 189 Temple St, Jordan, Hong Kong
result.name: Fusion Kitchen Restaurant & Bar

reviews.text:
The menu has all sorts of dishes, from Indian curries to pizza. 
A couple of table (perhaps regulars) are enjoying themselves but in an inclusive way: one guy shares a beer jug with guests at other tables. In the back a guy plays guitar; occasionally guests sing along in Nepalese. The space is Hong Kong cozy but not loud or sweaty.

My hotel is right up from Temple Street and after a long day out I wanted to find a good dinner close by that was something different than the dim sum from the night before. I remembered seeing some restaurants tucked off to the side of the Night Market so I walked that way and found Fusion. I got chicken curry and naan and it was really delicious. Lots of chicken, awesome flavor in the curry sauce/gravy and the naan went along perfectly. Every table was filled while I was there. They offer a large selection of beers and other foods aside from curry as well. Friendly staff, good atmosphere, and good food. I’ve got no complaints!
Fusion Kitchen with its mini bar really a suitable place for silent lovers..

reviews.text: It's okay. The pizza here is good although not extraordinary . Good place if you're vegan.

The food is delicious and the service is good. The price of lunch set is reasonable. The lunch set included soup, main course and drink. The curry and kebab are tasty. Recommend for those who would like to like something different.
The food is sooooo delicious! And not to mention the waiter and waitresses are very polite and patient. 😊
Very good very good! Nice service tasty food and they treat you like friends!
A bit expensive but the food is delicious.  I like the crispy thing they serve at the beginning! The sauce is very good as well.

result.name: 小酒窩餐廳

html_attributions: 小酒窩餐廳 V Dimpal Fusion and Pizza House

reviews.text:
我要了一份咖哩魚+烤餅，因為有很多香料，味道較濃，很有異國風味，有點去旅行的感覺，而且環境舒適，值得再去。
但……若其他客人不喜歡聽印度的音樂和歌曲，也不要播中文歌好嗎？異國風味大減喇!
晚餐接近7點就滿座，很好吃，份量不錯，服務不錯，環境一般，廁所可以。

好似嗌左七樣菜式
掛住食而且係秒清 淨係影得一張相
調味料落得重手但係唔會太鹹仲好惹味
All dishes we tried were delicious!
Seasoning was heavy but it didn't went too salty. It was savory and we emptied the plates as fast as tornado does.
ピザあり、パスタあり、インドカレーあり、ケバブあり、酒は各種あり。イタリアとインドとトルコのフュージョン料理という感じです。味は少し濃いめですが、野菜は新鮮で美味しくいただきました。店員は英語話してフレンドリー。
好味。服務好。羊肉卷、吞拿魚沙律、黑松露带子意大利飯、白汁濶麪條、 咖哩牛肉、咖哩羊肉，還有薄餅都好吃。今天忘記手機先食。
